translations: v．（鸟）唧唧叫，啾啾叫：指鸟发出轻柔的叫声。
· The baby birds were cheeping in their nest.

sentences.sentence: But everywhere the singing birds are cheeping.
sentences.translation: 但到处有唱着歌儿的鸟儿在吱吱叫。

sentences.sentence: One farmer said that it was "good for nothing but to raise cheeping squirrels on."
sentences.translation: 有一个农夫说这地“毫无用处，只好养一些叽叽叫的松鼠”。
